."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Our role is to identify industry gaps, design scalable SaaS systems, build the underlying technology, and support the long-term growth of each product company."}]]}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"lu-section bg-white px-6 py-24 lg:px-12","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"mx-auto max-w-7xl","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-12 max-w-3xl","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"lu-eyebrow mb-4","children":"Operating Philosophy"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#071330] md:text-5xl","children":"We build, operate, and evolve product companies."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2","children":[["$","article","Long-term platform ownership",{"className":"lu-card p-8","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-[#10277a]","children":"Long-term platform ownership"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-7 text-slate-600","children":"We build product ecosystems with the expectation that they will be operated, improved, and supported over many years."}]]}],["$","article","Industry-specific architecture",{"className":"lu-card p-8","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-[#10277a]","children":"Industry-specific architecture"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-7 text-slate-600","children":"Each platform is shaped around a real operating environment rather than a generic software category."}]]}],["$","article","Practical innovation",{"className":"lu-card p-8","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-[#10277a]","children":"Practical innovation"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-7 text-slate-600","children":"AI, IoT, automation, and data systems are introduced where they improve concrete platform capability."}]]}],["$","article","Product company separation",{"className":"lu-card p-8","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-[#10277